{
  "ref": "snowball-champion",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Snowball champion",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Before starting the third game",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Another contender for the podium!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "There's a podium?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Sadly not, I just say that because it sounds cool."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Let's wait a bit for the other games to finish up."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Now they are starting to trickle in, the game will start shortly!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Hey, haven't we met before?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "No, no, must have been another dwarf, plenty round these parts."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Hmm... Well I hope you both brought your snow boots, it's going to be carnage."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Pssssst [player name]."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "PSSSST [player name]."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Let's talk strategy, come here."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I don't hear any foul play going on, do I?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "No of course not, I'm just playing mind games with poor [player name]. They have no chance."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "You cheeky little..."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "When down to two final champions",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "We are down to our last two finalists."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "This calls for one thing and one thing only..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Sudden."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Death."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Snowball."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "I'm so very scared of [player name]."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "The rules are as follows."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "You each get one snowball each to throw."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Whomever get's hit first, is out."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Do you both understand the rules?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Guss?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Yes!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "[player name]?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Yes sir."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Coming at you [player name]."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Oh no..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "What are you playing at dwarf! I haven't even started the countdown."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "My bad... I'm just very eager."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Also, you didn't even go for [player name]. What's that about?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Honestly... I'm just an awful shot."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Could've sworn a dwarf in a previous festive games final did the same thing and knocked me clean out."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Then proceeded to sneak into the pub."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Ha, you don't say."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Moving on..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I'll ignore you ever did that."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "On the count of three, you will both be able to throw a snowball."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "One..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Two..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Three!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Snowball!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Is that a golden sn-"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Oof!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Wooo!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "There we have it folks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Our Festive Games champion!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Guss..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Mmmmistletoad!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Who are you talking to?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "That's not important. You just won the Festive games!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Oh my!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "I don't know what to say."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "You now get access to..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "The Nutcracker pub!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Alongside your win, you also get a free plus one to take into the pub with you!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Did you hear that [player name]?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "[player name] we can go into the pub together!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "[player name]...?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Ehem, [player name]...?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Oh dear."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Guss Mistletoad",
                  "text": "Fancy a pint?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I though't you'd never ask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Gosh, my head hurts."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I better see how Guss is getting on."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After completing the event",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "How's it going [player name]?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I'm alright, but I'm rather chilly round this part of the pub."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "You'll get used to it."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Do you enjoy doing all this?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Eh... It's alright I suppose."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "You don't really like it then?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "It's not that I don't like it, moreso that I'm on a journey of redemption."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Oh yeah?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I wasn't the most friendly Fremennik before I came here."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I did many awful things..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Shoo-ing away stray dogs."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Sacrificing cats in West Ardougne."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Stealing snow and making my own snowcone business."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "The list goes on."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I hope you didn't sell the golden snowballs."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Also... You did WHAT to stray dogs?!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Sorry.. I didn't mean to snap. You are on your journey to redeem yourself."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "That I am, [player name]"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Tell me about yourself."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Well, there's not much to tell really."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I used to take part in great big snowball tournaments around Gielinor."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I won every single one."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I was unstoppable."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Some might say there was snow stopping you."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Oh dear..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I was an awful person back then... Didn't make time for anyone. It was all about winning."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I missed my pet rock's first birthday, what kind of person does that?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "I was a monster..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "The last thing I remember before getting this gig with Santa was me trying to help someone."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Apparently I tried to save some Gnome children from a catastrophic avalanche to the north."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Next thing I knew, I was talking to Santa and he asked me to come to The Nutcracker."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Wow, so now you're on your journey to be a better person?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "Yup, though I do get thorough enjoyment watching people being pelted with snowballs."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Happy Holidays!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Snowball champion",
                  "text": "You too [player name]."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}